{"tid":1655156,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國要求數萬名記者參加「習思想」在線考試","createTime":"2019-10-15T02:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T11:47:38.000Z","uid":56881,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1691084d61ec12fa2369261854b837f6745b4292","tid":1655156,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:33:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://yahoo-news.com.hk/BBCChineseNews/6801/?yptr=yahoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyahoo-news.com.hk%2FBBCChineseNews%2F6801%2F%3Fyptr%3Dyahoo&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9DeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=60acbfe5\" target=\"_blank\">https://yahoo-news.com.hk/BBCChineseNews/6801/?yptr=yahoo</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://c.files.bbci.co.uk/49C6/production/_98168881_chinacensorship4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc.files.bbci.co.uk%2F49C6%2Fproduction%2F_98168881_chinacensorship4.jpg&h=875c8c01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBBC<br />\n「黨的新聞輿論工作的職責和使命是什麼？」<br />\n<br />\n如果你選擇了「牢牢堅持新聞真實」，手機屏幕上會迅速出現一個錯誤符號，提示正確答案應當是「牢牢堅持正面宣傳為主」。<br />\n<br />\n中國官方手機應用「學習強國」<br />\n裏「新聞採編學習」欄目下的一道練習題，中國數以萬計的記者們在過去一個月內都在緊鑼密鼓地對該題庫進行溫習。<br />\n<br />\n因為11月前，他們將正式參加一場全國性的在線考試，以測試他們對黨的政策及主席習近平的忠誠度。不參加考試或沒有考過的記者將無法換發新的記者證。<br />\n<br />\n在線考試<br />\n考試的消息在上周五（10月11日）獲得了證實。在一份官方發佈的名為《關於開展2019年新聞採編人員崗位培訓考試的通知》中，中國國家新聞出版署稱中國將在全國範圍內，進行新聞單位採編人員的崗位培訓考試。<br />\n<br />\n這將是中國官方首次要求新聞採編人員參加統一的在線考試。<br />\n根據通知，考試人員包括全國的通訊社、廣播電台、電視台、期刊與報社的人員。<br />\n<br />\n根據要求，考試需要在10月28日至11月10日完成，各媒體可以自行決定考試時間。《南華早報》此前報道稱，來自北京14個官方媒體的約一萬名記者和編輯，被要求在十月初提前參加「試點考試」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c.files.bbci.co.uk/133A/production/_109222940_133.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc.files.bbci.co.uk%2F133A%2Fproduction%2F_109222940_133.jpg&h=03100d29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBBC<br />\n成千上萬的中國記者將在11月前參加「學習強國」的在線考試。<br />\n<br />\n蠣螛了我的蟈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81bdfea9682b60bd79cb24696e63282d4cfa7ea4","tid":1655156,"uid":178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:38:40.000Z","msg":"厲害了你的支"},{"pid":"0ea8da5e706c355406f65dcb2578ac28be8b0beb","tid":1655156,"uid":2718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T03:13:36.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445649e260781ae07defb9f182899f651f0d207d","tid":1655156,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:55:33.000Z","msg":"正常"},{"pid":"0b8bbb34f2beddc0a102a39a01c538629bd09ec2","tid":1655156,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:59:15.000Z","msg":"這就是支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369413c7f37b6d46eb87f66e4730ad24e8a3e5b5","tid":1655156,"uid":53463,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:59:39.000Z","msg":"性感主席在線出題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98fec2e63cc6e52976517cb46bc1ec10c46f4c66","tid":1655156,"uid":69899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7436a8f9c6f878bac4f8d4b344ab52764e2180b4","tid":1655156,"uid":35342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd72375f7dfb243ad97732aef29e134570a00b6","tid":1655156,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:04:38.000Z"